OL,3,CGareth Bale part of rejected group bid
OL,4,Cto buy Cardiff City
OL,6,FGareth Bale is part of a United States
OL,7,Finvestment group hoping to buy League
OL,8,FOne club Cardiff City, according to
OL,9,Freports.
OL,11,FThe 35-year-old former Wales Captain
OL,12,Fis understood to be part of a
OL,13,Fconsortium that approached current
OL,14,FBluebirds owner Vincent Tan with a
OL,15,Fletter of intent to buy the club last
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,18,FThe Athletic reports that the letter
OL,19,Fincluded financial figures but the bid
OL,20,Fwas rejected. Cardiff declined to
OL,21,Fcomment on Friday night.
